</p>

<h3>Activity 2: The Great Lift Debate</h3>
<p>In this activity children pick their own way through a choose your own adventure in user requirements.
    <br />The scenario is based on a true story about the early days of lifts in the skyscrapers of New York.</p>
<p>
    <a href="~/Images/UserExperience_SessionPlan40.pdf">Lesson plan</a>
