</p>


<h3>Activity 3: But What Do We Do?</h3> 
<p>In this activity the childrena re faced with an insurmountable task, to design the keys for a 2 player game without any documentation. The aim is for it to become clear that this is not possible, and for the the children to gain a first hand understanding of how the use documentation impacts the design decisions of the game. </p>
<p>This is a double activity for which there is a double lesson plans and 2 worksheets.</p>
